  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you cast a spell that deals acid, cold, fire, lightning, poison, or thunder damage, you can spend 2 sorcery points to select a number of affected creatures up to your Charisma modifier (minimum of one creature). To select a creature, it must have failed its saving throw against the spell (if the spell required a saving throw).</p>\n<p>For the next minute, the selected creatures take 1d10 damage of the spell's damage type at the beginning of each of their turns. A creature can use an action to end this effect on themselves or another creature within 5 feet.</p>",
